An incredibly delicious and addictive drink!
The ingredients on the label are strange but surely it's safe.
name: Z-Cola

A special soap that \n[2] likes to bathe with.
It smells like flowers.
name: Erotic Soap

An memo that allows me to compete in The Violet Cup!
Misty's handwriting is really pretty...
name: Misty's Endorsement

A crazy looking fish that's glowing bright green!
It's probably not safe to eat but maybe I can sell it.
name: Nuclear Fish

name: Golden Fish

Ouch! This fish is incredibly hot to the touch!
It's probably not safe to eat but maybe I can sell it.
name: Magma Fish
